                                     <p style="margin-bottom: 1em">Have you ever had ads stalk you across the net? One minute you're shopping for pants; the next minute ads for pants are popping up on every site you visit!</p>

                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em">Advertising networks have hidden tracks on most internet sites. Google alone has trackers on 75% of the top million sites! Unless you prevent it, you're being tracked on all these sites. Then, your profile is made available for advertisers to bid on, allowing them to target you with their ads wherever you go:</p>
